data.description: Great value! Spacious ranch with newer hardwood floors,all wood windows,three seasons room with stone floor.Two car side load garage. Almost one acre lot with many mature trees. New metal roof, SOLAR PANELS, 3 fireplaces, furnace and ac unit replaced 2021. Added 4 large rooms to basement, updated kitchen appliances and appearance new vinyl flooring.
data.whatILove: This home is almost self sufficient and has the options of both gas and electric, solar panels, and it’s own water supply and septic , in a great school system, close to everything you would want and yet just out of the city limits for no city tax
